{"tid":563441,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：一向履行合約精神","createTime":"2018-02-17T02:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T11:45:47.000Z","uid":31314,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ec8161c65d62b43a74ec90316ee9eed8ecf4b0","tid":563441,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家能夠想像不是由雲加執教的阿仙奴嗎？沒有雲加的阿仙奴還是阿仙奴嗎？</span></strong></span>至少在餘下這1年半，雲加仍會繼續領軍。<br />\n<br />\n在位多年的領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）去年夏天與阿仙奴簽下為期兩年的新合約，現時仍餘下約1年半，本應無需過早考慮去留；不過，球隊上季意外錯過歐聯參賽資格後，今季仍未見起色，甚有機會連續兩個球季跌出聯賽前4以外，部份人開始懷疑，雲加或會在今個夏天就掛冠而去。 不過，68歲的雲加接受《beIN Sports》專訪時，親口粉碎外界揣測：「我一直以來都有履行合約精神；我想提醒你，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為了履行我的合約，我拒絕過世界上所有最大的球會，而我亦嘗試一直繼續下去。</strong></span>」 雲加續道：「在這個職業，未來就是未來發生的事。但對我來說，那是要贏出下一場比賽。球隊每一仗都應該踢得更好，展示出對勝利的渴求&mdash;&mdash;直至球季結束。這就是球隊的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5a8c62408e7c92544bb1f4b84e0486e06cfcab4b","tid":563441,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc737be1dc7c372ab9eeffde0acf1f3ff9b8f3de","tid":563441,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"開始迷雲了"},{"pid":"26f5af389169309ef355024518f2eb38f286592a","tid":563441,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"如果有一個人對阿仙奴忠誠<br />\n<br />\n果個就是我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p